sub_title: Coordinator Online Communications at Groninger Museum
summary:
Art historian managing the Groninger Museum online presence with an eye for copy writing, content creation, strategic content planning and visitor participation. 

Specialities: museums, art education, online strategy & cross media communication, writing for web and social media, online marketing campaigns, e-mailmarketing, ticketing & narrowcasting. 

I’m interested in: storytelling, innovation, technology and all things that enhance learning processes.
